comments: Hardaway Jr. (DAL) makes contact to Leonard's (LAC) arm during the drive to the basket that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Harrell (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position during Doncic's (DAL) driving shot attempt.
Leonard (LAC) and Kleber (DAL) briefly engage in marginal contact off ball prior to separating.
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Williams' (LAC) path and he is firming up over his left leg when the contact occurs during the pick.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) and Shamet (LAC) briefly engage in marginal contact off ball prior to separating.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) briefly places two hands on Leonard (LAC) during the drive but he immediately removes his hands. The contact is marginal.
Porzingis (DAL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Leonard (LAC) after the release of the ball during his shot attempt.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) swipes down and does not make contact to Harrell's (LAC) arm during his shot attempt near the rim.

Leonard (LAC) and Hardaway Jr. (DAL) arrive at the ball simultaneously. Leonard places two hands on the ball and makes clean contact with it during the tie up with Hardaway Jr. (DAL). A jump ball should have been assessed.
As a progressing player, Finney-Smith (DAL) gathers the loose ball on his left foot and takes three steps prior to coming to a stop.
Leonard (LAC) initiates marginal foot to foot contact with Doncic (DAL) during his drive. Doncic moves through the contact and continues his drive.
Harrell (LAC) maintains a legal guarding position on Finney-Smith (DAL) during the drive.
Finney-Smith's (DAL) left foot steps out of bounds prior to completely releasing the ball during his pass attempt.
Wright (DAL) briefly places a hand on the opposite side of Green's (LAC) body. Wright immediately slides his hand off as he cleanly deflects the pass intended for Green. The contact is marginal.
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on Green (LAC).
Shamet (LAC) commits a take foul on Doncic (DAL).
Porzingis (DAL) commits a take foul on Leonard (LAC).
